.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, sprite, water
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, prince, oliveros, dannemann
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, indie, salsa, trance
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goldfish, rabbit
 1. the fan of salsa is between the owner of the dog and the fan of indie##2
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
 4. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
 5. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the fan of indie##8
 6. the dannemann-smoker is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 7. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of house is the owner of the frog##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
11. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
12. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
13. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the prince-smoker##5
14. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
16. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
17. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
18. the prince-smoker is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
19. the person drinking water is on the right of the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | sprite | water  | milk  |
| Cigar          | dannemann     | prince | chaman | oliveros  |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | salsa  | trance | house |
| Pet           | goldfish | rabbit | dog    | frog  |

