.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, soy-milk, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, chess, magic-tricks, skydiving
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, yellow, aquamarine, pink
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, british, german, italian
 1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the italian##1
 2. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
 3. the person drinking sprite is the person who likes yellow##1
 4. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 5. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person who likes pink##5
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the person who likes white##8
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 8. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the german##3
 9. the british is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
10. the person who likes aquamarine is not the brazilian##6
11. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
12. the italian is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the person who likes pink is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
14. the brazilian is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | cola      | sprite  | soy-milk | juice        |
| Hobby         | skydiving | chess   | baking   | magic-tricks |
| Color   | pink    | yellow   | aquamarine    | white      |
| Nationality   | british   | italian | german   | brazilian    |

