.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, milk, sprite
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, lemon, lime, avocado
4 different pets are kept: goat, hedgehog, pony, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter, subway, van
 1. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 2. the owner of the snake is not to the right of the person eating lemon##8
 3. the owner of the goat is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the owner of the pony##5
 6. the person driving the van is the person drinking juice##1
 7. the person eating avocado is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
 8. the person eating lime is on the far right##1
 9. the person eating lemon is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
10. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
12. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
13. the person driving the subway is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1        |    2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | juice          | iced-tea | milk        | sprite    |
| Food         | avocado | pomegranate   | lemon | lime  |
| Pet         | pony           | goat     | snake       | hedgehog  |
| Transport   | van            | subway   | scooter     | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, lemonade, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, card-games, puzzles, rock-climbing
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, fisherman, photographer, project-manager
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, blues, disco, pop
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the person drinking lemonade##6
 2. the dancer is not to the left of the fan of pop##8
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the fan of blues##1
 4. the dancer is not to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
 5. the fisherman is somewhere to the right of the photographer##5
 6. the fan of disco is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 8. the person drinking coffee is not to the left of the photographer##8
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
10. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the fan of pop and the project-manager##7
11. the fan of disco is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |      2       |       3       |    4    |
| Beverage    | lemonade        | fanta        | coffee        | water   |
| Hobby       | card-games      | camping      | rock-climbing | puzzles |
| Job         | project-manager | photographer | fisherman     | dancer  |
| Music-Genre   | disco          | reggae      | blues     | pop  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, singing, sudoku
4 different games are played: chess, mah-jongg, poker, scrabble
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, romance, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, indie, jazz, reggae
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person playing chess##8
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 3. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
 4. the person playing scrabble is the person watching western movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person playing poker##6
 6. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
 7. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the person playing poker##8
 8. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
 9. the fan of jazz is in an even position##4
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
11. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person playing poker and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
13. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku    | singing   | board-games   | collecting |
| Game           | chess | mah-jongg    | poker | scrabble    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | adventure | animation     | western    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | jazz      | indie         | reggae     |

 